00:39:07,633 --> 00:39:09,333
[ Background Music ]

745
00:39:09,333 --> 00:39:14,567
Hey. [ Laughter ]

746
00:39:14,567 --> 00:39:25,533
[ Background Music ]

747
00:39:25,533 --> 00:39:33,600
[ Stirring ]

748
00:39:33,600 --> 00:39:35,600
[ Background Music ]

749
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:38,267
Do you want a pancake? >>
Breakfast?

750
00:39:38,267 --> 00:39:39,667
Yeah, do you want one?

751
00:39:39,667 --> 00:39:43,933
I have two ready for you
right here.

752
00:39:43,933 --> 00:39:46,233
Thanks. You can eat it.

753
00:39:46,233 --> 00:39:49,433
We already had the prayer.

754
00:39:49,433 --> 00:39:51,067
What time did you all get
up?

755
00:39:51,067 --> 00:39:52,833
6:30.

756
00:39:52,833 --> 00:39:55,567
What have you been doing
since 6:30?

757
00:39:55,567 --> 00:39:57,633
The usual; prayer,
scriptures,

758
00:39:57,633 --> 00:39:59,700
chores, and now breakfast.

759
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:01,567
But it's barely 9.

760
00:40:01,567 --> 00:40:03,133
Yeah, we slept in a little
today.

761
00:40:03,133 --> 00:40:05,367
We usually get up at 6 o'clock
so we're all done

762
00:40:05,367 --> 00:40:07,467
with breakfast by 8:30.

763
00:40:07,467 --> 00:40:09,367
Where is my mom?

764
00:40:09,367 --> 00:40:11,133
I haven't seen her up yet.

765
00:40:11,133 --> 00:40:12,800
What about Brendan?

766
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,633
He should be probably
playing out in the playhouse.

767
00:40:14,633 --> 00:40:17,167
He's so lucky.

768
00:40:17,167 --> 00:40:25,200
[ Background Music ]

769
00:40:25,200 --> 00:40:27,933
What? Are you here for tea
party?

770
00:40:27,933 --> 00:40:29,667
What are you doing today?
