his two-seat truck.

772
00:40:31,233 --> 00:40:32,400
There's no room for you.

773
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,467
Ride in the back?

774
00:40:33,467 --> 00:40:35,767
Nope. Have fun.

775
00:40:35,767 --> 00:41:07,733
[ Background Music ]

776
00:41:07,733 --> 00:41:15,733
Jacob, Sarah, dinner duty.

777
00:41:15,733 --> 00:41:17,133
