778
00:41:17,133 --> 00:41:19,667
Setting and clearing the
table.

779
00:41:19,667 --> 00:41:22,300
Jacob, it is your night to
help me fix dinner.

780
00:41:22,300 --> 00:41:24,067
Could I help? Sure.

781
00:41:24,067 --> 00:41:25,600
Go wash your hands and I'll
get you started

782
00:41:25,600 --> 00:41:29,267
