786
00:41:38,367 --> 00:41:42,767
Tell me about it. Move.

787
00:41:42,767 --> 00:41:49,533
[ Background Music ]

788
00:41:49,533 --> 00:41:51,133
Amen.

789
00:41:51,133 --> 00:41:53,333
